[msg MSG_000_0_0 [Mr. Edogawa]]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 1 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14823 0 0]What brings you to the nurse's office? Eeeheehee...[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]My, you want another of my supplementary lessons? You are the quintessential student...[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]Or, could it be...?[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14814 0 0]Ah, don't worry, I was just talking to myself.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]So, what do you want to review?[n][uf 1 1][e]

[sel SEL_001_0_0 top]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1]Tarot procedures[e]
