[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1]Advanced readings[e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1]Never mind[e]

[msg MSG_002_0_0 [Mr. Edogawa]]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14801 0 0]Well then, I'll tell you once again about the procedure for a standard tarot reading.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]For now, let's keep to the simple one-card spread, where you draw and interpret a single card.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]It will suffice for learning the basic methods of the tarot.[n][uf 1 1][e]

[msg MSG_002_1_0 [Mr. Edogawa]]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14805 0 0]Now, a quick word on the deck... For the best results, you'll want to use all 78 cards.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]But for this explanation, we'll limit ourselves to the 22 Major Arcana.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]The procedure for telling fortunes via the tarot goes like so: shuffle, cut, spread, and read.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14816 0 0]That means mixing them all up, putting them in a pile, lining up the drawn cards, and examining them.[n][uf 1 1][e]

[msg MSG_002_2_0 [Mr. Edogawa]]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]When I say "spread," I refer to how they will be presented. It's a concept I'll come back to several times.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]...Ah, I nearly forgot about the necessary preparation before handling the cards.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14804 0 0]Before one begins a tarot reading, one's mind must be calm.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]Try to simultaneously unify and relax your consciousness.[n][uf 1 1][e]

[msg MSG_002_3_0 [Mr. Edogawa]]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]You must also stay focused on the goal of your reading, to avoid wishful thinking clouding the result.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14807 0 0]Once you're relaxed, we'll begin.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]Place the cards facedown on the table to hide their images...[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]Then the client of the reading will shuffle, or mix, the cards.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14814 0 0]If you're reading your own fortune, then you perform this step yourself.[n][uf 1 1][e]

[msg MSG_002_4_0 [Mr. Edogawa]]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]The most common method is to spread them on the table, mixing them in a circular motion with your left hand.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]The left hand is the agent of the subconscious mind, you see. Eeeheehee...[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14816 0 0]Though if you're clumsy, or have lost a hand, or what have you, you can use either or both hands. It all depends.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]When the client is satisfied, make a single pile, and thus complete the shuffling phase.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]A "pile" meaning a neat, orderly stack. You remember this, don't you?[n][uf 1 1][e]

[msg MSG_002_5_0 [Mr. Edogawa]]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14806 0 0]Now, on to cutting the deck.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]Split the stack you've made into three piles, each roughly the same height.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]Normally the client also performs the cut, but the fortune-teller is free to perform this step as well.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14803 0 0]Just allow the spirit to move you.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]It may be your own feelings, and it may be occult inspiration...[n][uf 1 1][e]

[msg MSG_002_6_0 [Mr. Edogawa]]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]Reorganize the three piles in the order of your choosing, and combine them into one pile again.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14815 0 0]Once this is complete, the reader should take the pile.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]Be very careful during this step. You must preserve the direction the cards originally faced.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]If the client is someone else, turn the pile so the cards face the same direction that they were to you.[n][uf 1 1][e]

[msg MSG_002_7_0 [Mr. Edogawa]]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14804 0 0]And now, it's finally time to draw a card. This is the spread phase.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]We're doing a one-card spread, so turn over the top card, and place it on the field to the side.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]In some methods, you specify which card from the top... But that's a topic for another time.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14816 0 0]The card on the field provides the answer to the client's question.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]Now, at last, the reading phase.[n][uf 1 1][e]

[msg MSG_002_8_0 [Mr. Edogawa]]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]First, we must understand the card's meaning.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14814 0 0]What the card represents depends on if it's reversed or not...[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]You do remember that much, yes?[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]There are a few exceptions, but in general, a reversed card is negative, and has a different meaning.[n][uf 1 1][e]

[msg MSG_002_9_0 [Mr. Edogawa]]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14806 0 0]Once you understand the meaning of the card drawn, apply it to your question...[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]Let inspiration rise to the surface of your mind, and... well...[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]Form a story around it![n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14803 0 0]Regardless, simply telling the client the card's meaning isn't considered a true reading.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]Using the clue derived from the card, the reader must use their inspiration to look into the client's future.[n][uf 1 1][e]

[msg MSG_003_0_0 [Mr. Edogawa]]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]It's important to converse with the client as well, to assist with your divinations.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14807 0 0]Tarot is about both reading the cards and reading people.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]As for the meaning of each card, look them up on your own time. Eeeheehee...[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]And that's all we covered on the basic procedures of tarot readings.[n][uf 1 1][e]

[msg MSG_003_5_0 [Mr. Edogawa]]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14814 0 0]My throat's starting to hurt, so come back later if you want to hear about another subject.[n][uf 1 1][e]

[msg MSG_004_0_0 [Mr. Edogawa]]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14801 0 0]I'll tell you again about how to use all 78 Major and Minor Arcana, as well as the basic spread.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]To review, the tarot is made of 22 Major Arcana and 56 Minor Arcana...[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]For a total of 78 cards. Is that clear?[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14816 0 0]Each card has its own inherent meaning.[n][uf 1 1][e]

[msg MSG_004_1_0 [Mr. Edogawa]]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]Many are daunted by the full deck, because of the sheer amount of cards... but take heart![n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]It is difficult to learn all the meanings, but having them all actually makes your reading easier.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14804 0 0]The more details one has available, the easier it is to craft a story...[n][uf 1 1][e]

[msg MSG_004_3_0 [Mr. Edogawa]]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]I already explained the Major Arcana, so let me give you an outline of the Minor Arcana.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]The Minor Arcana are divided into four classes, called suits.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14814 0 0]Do you recall when I told you that this is what common playing cards were modeled after?[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]The Wands, Cups, Swords, and Coins correspond to Clubs, Hearts, Spades, and Diamonds.[n][uf 1 1][e]

[msg MSG_004_4_0 [Mr. Edogawa]]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]Each suit has 10 numbered cards, ranging from Ace to 10...[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14803 0 0]As well as four face cards—King, Queen, Knight, and Page—unlike the three face cards in common decks.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]The Page is sometimes called Prince, though he's essentially a knight in training.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]The four face cards are called court cards. That term will come up again, so remember it well.[n][uf 1 1][e]

[msg MSG_004_5_0 [Mr. Edogawa]]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14805 0 0]There are 14 types in total, between the pip cards or number cards, and the face or court cards.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]These 14 types have four cards each, for a total of 56 cards in the Minor Arcana.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]And now you know the makeup of the Minor Arcana. As for how to use them in a reading...[n][uf 1 1][e]

[msg MSG_004_6_0 [Mr. Edogawa]]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14804 0 0]It's actually the same as the Major Arcana.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]Keep in mind the meaning of each card and the direction it faces, and use your inspiration to create a story.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]In the Minor Arcana, each suit, number, and court type has its own meaning.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14816 0 0]One of the best ways to memorize these is to imagine them in a 4-by-14 grid.[n][uf 1 1][e]

[msg MSG_004_7_0 [Mr. Edogawa]]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]And now, each of the four suits' meanings, in brief...[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]Wands for planning and growth, Cups for love and sentiment, Swords for trials, and Coins for wealth.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14804 0 0]As for the basic meaning of each of the numbered cards...[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]Ace is the beginning, 2 is balance, 3 is growth, 4 is stability, 5 is change, 6 is balance again...[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]7 is a new start, 8 is success, 9 is attainment, and 10 marks a terminus, or the end.[n][uf 1 1][e]

[msg MSG_004_8_0 [Mr. Edogawa]]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14803 0 0]Court cards represent people and their strengths. It could be the client, or other people involved.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]The Page represents children, and the offering of knowledge. The Knight is youth and boundless energy.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]The Queen represents adult women, while the King represents mature men.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14816 0 0]It's said that to grasp the meaning of the cards, it's important to communicate with them...[n][uf 1 1][e]

[msg MSG_004_9_0 [Mr. Edogawa]]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]Now then, let's move on to the method of using the full Arcana to tell fortunes.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]The basic procedure is the same... You'll just be using more cards.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14805 0 0]Even with the full deck of 78, you must first shuffle, then cut, spread, and read.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]The type of spread you use affects the procedure more than the number of cards in use.[n][uf 1 1][e]

[msg MSG_005_0_0 [Mr. Edogawa]]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]Now, for a change of subject... I'll explain the various types of spreads.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14803 0 0]First, remember that the spread is chosen according to the nature of the question.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]Do you want an answer to a single question? Or maybe an overview of the general future?[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]Use the spread that best fits the request you have in mind.[n][uf 1 1][e]

[msg MSG_005_3_0 [Mr. Edogawa]]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14804 0 0]For example, if you want to tell the client's past, present, and future...[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]Why not use a three-card spread, where you simply lay out three cards?[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]Adding a card produces the four-card spread, identifying the past, present, nature of the problem, and future.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14805 0 0]If you use the seven-card hexagram spread, with a single card placed in the center of a hexagon...[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]You can read both the nature of the problem and a countermeasure against it.[n][uf 1 1][e]

[msg MSG_005_5_0 [Mr. Edogawa]]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]There is also a spread called Question and Answer, involving two choices.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14816 0 0]This reading is done by setting two countermeasures against the question.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]Finally, the most well-known spread is the classic Celtic Cross.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]It's suited to telling fortunes with only the Major Arcana, and is used often by both beginners and experts.[n][uf 1 1][e]

[msg MSG_005_6_0 [Mr. Edogawa]]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14803 0 0]Arrange two cards crossing each other in the center, then one more on all four sides of the cross...[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]Then, place a pillar of four cards, known as the Spear of Destiny, next to it to the right.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]The cross of six cards represents the overall situation, with the four to the right making it concrete.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14804 0 0]Again, this forms the 10-card spread known as the Celtic Cross.[n][uf 1 1][e]

[msg MSG_005_7_0 [Mr. Edogawa]]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]There are other spreads, like the Horseshoe, Witch's Diamond, or the Seven Candles of Life...[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]And also the normal, triangle, and cross spreads.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14816 0 0]I remember telling you there were far too many types of spreads to go into detail on all of them.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]And that concludes my lecture on the Major and Minor Arcana, plus the basic types of spreads.[n][uf 1 1][e]

[msg MSG_005_9_0 [Mr. Edogawa]]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14814 0 0]Pluto calls, so you'll have to ask me about the other lectures next time.[n][uf 1 1][e]

[msg MSG_006_0_0 [Mr. Edogawa]]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14801 0 0]Since you seem interested in hearing it again, we'll go over advanced tarot readings.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]Remember, it's about combining other forms of fortune telling with the tarot deck.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]The most well-known fusion with tarot is astrology.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14807 0 0]For example, there's the almost self-explanatory Horoscope Spread.[n][uf 1 1][e]

[msg MSG_006_1_0 [Mr. Edogawa]]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]After shuffling and cutting the full deck of 78...[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]Spread them in a circle consisting of 12 cards, then place one more in the center.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14804 0 0]The 12 in the outer circle correspond directly to the 12 signs of the zodiac, also known as Houses.[n][uf 1 1][e]

[msg MSG_006_2_0 [Mr. Edogawa]]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]Each House shows an answer to a different problem, such as family and work, marriage, friendship, and money.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]The card in the center represents your overall fortune.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14816 0 0]This spread has a variety of uses, since you can gain an overall understanding of life.[n][uf 1 1][e]

[msg MSG_006_3_0 [Mr. Edogawa]]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]Why don't we review the significator once again, too?[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]It's used by those more accustomed to reading the tarot, but...[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14815 0 0]Before shuffling, you choose one card that best fits the client's image and place it on the field.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]This is the significator.[n][uf 1 1][e]

[msg MSG_006_4_0 [Mr. Edogawa]]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]It's very effective in heightening the client's inspiration.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14814 0 0]Do you remember the court, or face, cards? The significator is selected from the Minor Arcana face cards.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]For a high schooler, the Page card would be best. For an adult, the Knight, King, or Queen would do it.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]More experienced readers may use one of the Major Arcana, but the court cards are suitable most of the time.[n][uf 1 1][e]

[msg MSG_006_5_0 [Mr. Edogawa]]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14804 0 0]Now, back to ways of fusing the tarot with other fortune-telling methods...[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]An even more advanced application would be to use it in conjunction with dowsing.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0]That would be using a pendulum to find what you're looking for.[n][uf 1 1][e]

